      "acceptanceCriteria": "Round-off and iterative convergence errors quantified and shown to be negligible relative to discretization error for all operating points.",
      "rationale": "Iterative convergence was monitored via residual norms (target 1e-6) but round-off error was not formally estimated. No floating-point sensitivity study was performed. Factor flagged as not-assessed due to absence of formal quantification; epistemic gap at MRL 5."
