      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sufficient experimental replicates to characterize biological and batch variability in hemolysis measurements; statistical power analysis documented.",
      "rationale": "Experimental hemolysis data were available from a single published dataset with three replicates per operating point. No statistical power analysis was performed to confirm adequacy of sample size for MRL 5 requirements. Biological variability across blood donors not characterized. Factor not-assessed."
