      "rationale": "COU simulations use patient-representative blood viscosity distributions that differ from the fixed bovine blood properties used in validation experiments. No formal equivalency mapping or bridging analysis was performed to justify the transfer of validation evidence to the COU. Factor not-assessed at MRL 5."
